on damage:
    victim is a mob:
        play sound "entity.player.big_fall" with volume 20 and pitch 200 to attacker
on death:
    victim is a zombie:
        play sound "entity.player.experienceup" with volume 20 and pitch 300 to attacker
        add {experience::%victim's uuid%} to {experience::%attacker%}
        send title "&a&l+ %{experience::%victim's uuid%}%" with subtitle "&6&l%{level::%attacker%}%&8 &8&l>> &8&a%{experience::%attacker%}%&7/&a%{required::%attacker%}%" to attacker for 1 seconds
on death:
